===Arceuus spellbook===
The [[demonbane spells]] of the [[Arceuus spellbook]] can only be cast on [[Demon (attribute)|demonic monsters]]. Magic attack bonus needs to be -64 or lower to always splash, and equipping a [[tome of fire]] or [[skull sceptre]] will make that more difficult to reach while saving runes. Weaker demonic monsters such as [[icefiend]]s and [[pyrefiend]]s are ideal given their low stats, however armour will need to maximise [[Magical melee]] while keeping Magic accuracy low enough to splash.

